<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Yuvaraj Govindarajan - Portfolio</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}
.text-royal {
    color: #0055ff;
}
.bg-royal {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0055ff, #0033cc);
    color: #ffffff;
}
.glass-nav {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.glass-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}
.glass-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 85, 255, 0.1);
}
.hero-section {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 80px;
}
.hero-blob {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10%;
    right: 5%;
    width: 40vw;
    height: 40vw;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,85,255,0.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 70%);
    z-index: -1;
    border-radius: 50%;
}
.section-padding {
    padding: 100px 0;
}
.btn-royal {
    background-color: #0055ff;
    color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
}
.btn-royal:hover {
    background-color: #0033cc;
    color: #ffffff;
    transform: scale(1.05);
}
.skill-badge {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    color: #0055ff;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 4px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 85, 255, 0.1);
}
.timeline {
    border-left: 2px solid #0055ff;
    padding-left: 30px;
    margin-left: 15px;
}
.timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -37px;
    top: 0;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #0055ff;
    border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0,85,255,0.2);
}
.fw-800 {
    font-weight: 800;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg fixed-top glass-nav">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-royal" href="#">YG.</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-toggle="target" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-blob"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000">
                <h1 class="display-2 fw-800 mb-3">Hi, I'm <span class="text-royal">Yuvaraj Govindarajan [cite: 14]</span>.</h1>
                <h2 class="h3 fw-light mb-4">Senior Relationship Manager [cite: 29] & SAAS Specialist [cite: 15]</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-5 text-muted">Passionate about leveraging tech solutions to enhance business efficiency and customer experience[cite: 26].</p>
                <a href="#experience" class="btn btn-royal">View My Work</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Professional Summary [cite: 16]</h2>
                <div class="mx-auto mt-2 mb-4" style="width: 60px; height: 3px; background-color: #0055ff;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8 text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <p class="fs-5">As a Senior Relationship Manager at Webtel Electrosoft, I specialize in building and maintaining strong client relationships while driving sales growth and customer satisfaction[cite: 17]. With a strategic approach, I manage key accounts, identify new business opportunities, and provide tailored IT solutions to meet client needs[cite: 18].</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="skills" class="section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Top Skills & Certifications [cite: 4, 7]</h2>
                <div class="mx-auto mt-2 mb-4" style="width: 60px; height: 3px; background-color: #0055ff;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <div class="col-12">
                <span class="skill-badge">Business-to-Business (B2B) [cite: 5]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">Collaboration Tools [cite: 5]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">Sales Development [cite: 6]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">C++ Crash Course [cite: 8]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">Front-End Web Development [cite: 9]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">Google Data Analytics [cite: 10]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">Python (Basics) [cite: 11]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">Artificial Intelligence [cite: 12]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">Predictive Analysis [cite: 12, 13]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">CRM [cite: 15]</span>
                <span class="skill-badge">Cloud Security [cite: 15]</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="experience" class="section-padding bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Professional Experience [cite: 27]</h2>
                <div class="mx-auto mt-2 mb-4" style="width: 60px; height: 3px; background-color: #0055ff;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="timeline">
                    
                    <div class="timeline-item glass-card p-4" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-royal">Senior Relationship Manager [cite: 29]</h4>
                        <h5 class="text-muted">Webtel Electrosoft Ltd [cite: 28] | June 2024 - Present [cite: 30]</h5>
                        <ul class="mt-3">
                            <li>Drove a 15% increase in sales revenue within the first six months[cite: 31].</li>
                            <li>Improved lead conversion rates by 10% through a new CRM strategy[cite: 32].</li>
                            <li>Cultivated and managed key client relationships, resulting in a 20% increase in repeat business[cite: 34, 35].</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="timeline-item glass-card p-4" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-royal">Portfolio Manager [cite: 39]</h4>
                        <h5 class="text-muted">Square Yards [cite: 38] | May 2023 - December 2023 [cite: 40]</h5>
                        <ul class="mt-3">
                            <li>Handling a team of 5 BDA's as a portfolio manager[cite: 42].</li>
                            <li>Maintaining a high Retention factor in team with 90% employee retention[cite: 43].</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="timeline-item glass-card p-4" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-royal">Business Development Associate [cite: 47]</h4>
                        <h5 class="text-muted">BYJU'S [cite: 46] | December 2021 - February 2023 [cite: 48]</h5>
                        <ul class="mt-3">
                            <li>Proficiency in cold calling with B2B as well as B2C[cite: 50].</li>
                            <li>Achieving sales targets on a weekly basis[cite: 53].</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="education" class="section-padding">
    <div class="container text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">Education [cite: 77]</h2>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-2 mb-5" style="width: 60px; height: 3px; background-color: #0055ff;"></div>
        <div class="glass-card p-5 d-inline-block text-start">
            <h4 class="fw-bold text-royal">Rajalakshmi Engineering College [cite: 78]</h4>
            <p class="fs-5 mb-0">Bachelor of Engineering, Electrical, Electronics and Communications Engineering [cite: 79]</p>
            <p class="text-muted">2014 - 2018 [cite: 79]</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="section-padding bg-royal">
    <div class="container text-center" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">Let's Connect [cite: 1]</h2>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-5">Open for B2B collaborations, cloud security solutions, and professional networking.</p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-4">
            <a href="mailto:yraj470@gmail.com" class="btn btn-light btn-lg rounded-pill px-4 text-royal fw-bold">Email Me [cite: 2]</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yuvaraj-govindarajan-" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold">LinkedIn [cite: 3]</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.js"></script>
<script>
AOS.init({
    duration: 800,
    once: true,
    offset: 100
});
document.querySelectorAll('.nav-link').forEach(anchor => {
    anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
            behavior: 'smooth'
        });
    });
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
